(Source: Sky News YouTube Screenshot) SIGN up for conservative daily post news alerts I saw a really great post on , outlining some of the odd facts surrounding the COVID-19 outbreak and the subsequent global actions that have taken place since the virus was first reported.

It made me think about some of the things that have happened and been revealed over the past few weeks… …like the World Health Organization’s lie that the virus wasn’t transmissible from human to human… …like the complete and utter economy-killing actions (stay-at home orders) the president was boxed into making (but democrat leaders were more than happy to exploit )… …like the deep state and Gates Foundation ties shared by Drs.

Fauci and Birx (who ‘advise’ President Trump and are looking at a whopping payday promoting a ‘vaccine’)… …like the strange millions of dollars that were approved to increase mail-in ballots and other attacks on election integrity… …like the fact that democrats used the outbreak to suddenly flood certain areas with released convicts… …like the fact that President Trump had to stop all rallies… …like the fact that the United Nations Agency WHO is using it to justify invading homes and “isolating” sick people… …like the fact that the media and WH ‘experts’ seem strangely upset that hydroxychloroquine is working to cure COVID-19 patients at an amazing rate.
All of these ‘results’ stem from one city in China.
Although I don’t want to encourage ‘conspiracy theories,’ there are three strange facts surrounding that Chinese ‘outbreak’ that simply don’t add up.
Indeed, they stink to high heaven.

Strange Spread of the Disease: Wuhan to Shanghai = 839km Wuhan to Beijing = 1,152km Wuhan to Milan = 15,000km Wuhan to NY = 15,000km Even today, India is locked down but all the cities of China are open .
The Coronavirus started in Wuhan yet there is no effect of Coronavirus in nearby Beijing or Shanghai but many deaths in Italy, Iran, European countries and USA.

The Coronavirus originated from the city of Wuhan in China and has now reached every corner of the world, but the virus did not reach China’s capital Beijing and China’s Economic Capital Shanghai, located in close proximity to Wuhan itself.
All business areas of China are now safe.
Another big thing is, that the worldwide share market has fallen by almost half.
In India also the Nifty has gone from 12 thousand to 7 thousand, but the share market of China was at 3000 and just merely dropped to 2700.

Hollywood stars, Australia’s Home Minister, Britain’s Prime Minister and Health Minister, Spain’s Prime Minister’s wife, Canada’s Prime Minister’s wife, and Britain’s Prince Charles, among others, have contracted the Coronavirus, but NOT A SINGLE POLITICAL LEADER IN CHINA, NOT A SINGLE MILITARY COMMANDER in China have tested positive for Coronavirus.
The only real conclusion here is that apparently the Chinese know something that the rest of the world does not about coronavirus .
